            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Hd1e108">Rubrica 1</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De odio</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>QUartus liber secunde partis
      <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>tractat de odio discordia et
      <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>pace: sub his titulis sequen
      <lb ed="#V" n="58" break="no"/>tibus.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e125">
               <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>
      ¶ De odio. Rubrica. i. 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e130">
               <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>¶
               <ref>Salomodo in prouerb. c. 10.</ref>
               <lb ed="#V" n="61"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e134">Odium suscitat rixas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e141">
               <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e145">/ 26 c. Qui operit odium fraudulenter reuela
        <lb ed="#V" n="63" break="no"/>bitur malitia eius in concilio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e151">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>¶
               <ref>Aristoteles rethoricorum li. 2. ca. 21.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e155">Non
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>oportet amare tanquam oditurum: sed magis
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>odire tanquam amaturum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e163">
               <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>¶
               <ref>Iesus filius sirach in eccl. c. 9.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e167">Temerarius
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>in verbo suo odibilis erit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e173">
               <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>¶
               <ref>Terentius in andria. c. 3.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e177">Ueritas odium
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>parit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e183">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>¶
               <ref>Tullius tusculanarum questionum li. 4.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e187">Odium
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>est ira inueterata.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e193">
               <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>¶
               <ref>Ouidius sine tituio siue amorum libro i. c. 8.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e197">Se
        <lb ed="#V" n="74" break="no"/>pe simultates ira morata facit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e204">
               <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>¶
               <ref>Quintilianus declam. i. declam.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e208">Odium omne
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>adurunt oculi: et hunc in pectoribus humanis
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>furentem lumina accendunt. Nec leuis animis
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>accidit insania quotiens quem execraris aspi
        <lb ed="#V" n="79" break="no"/>cias.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e220"> /
      <ref>10 declam.</ref>
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e222"><sic>Oodia</sic> plerumque ex inani
        <lb ed="#V" n="80" break="no"/>bus causis aboriuntur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e228"> /
      <ref>12 declam.</ref>
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e230">Non
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>adeo desunt odiorum cause: vt iam rara simul
        <lb ed="#V" n="82" break="no"/>tas sit: et vt videatur aliquis nihil magis quam ma
        <lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>los odisse.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e240"> /
      <ref>14 declam.</ref>
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e242">Omnia facinora nisi
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>fallor causas vel de cupiditate: vel de simul
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>tatibus trahunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e250">
               <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>¶
               <ref>Ioannes apostolus et euangels epistola vnica. c. i.</ref> 
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e254">Qui odit fratrem suum: in tenebris est: et in tene
        <lb ed="#V" n="88" break="no"/>bris ambulat: et nescit quo vadat: quoniam tene
        <lb ed="#V" n="89" break="no"/>bre obscurauerunt oculos eius. <!--112.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="43-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e271">
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>¶
               <ref>Iuuenalis li. 5. et fi. satis 3. et pe.</ref>     
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e275">Intur finitimos vetus atque antiqua simultas:
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>Immortale odium et nunquam sanabile vulnus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e284">
               <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>¶
               <ref>Claudianus li. 3.</ref>
                
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e288">Non odium terrore moues.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e294">
               <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>¶
               <ref>Fulgentius mitologiarum lib. i. fabum. 6.</ref> 
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e298">Mortalium iurgiorum inuidie ternario conflan
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>tur statu: id est namli: causali: accidentali. Natu
        <lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>rale est odium vt canium et luporum pecudum et lu
        <lb ed="#V" n="10" break="no"/>porum: hominum et serpentium. Casuale est vt amo
        <lb ed="#V" n="11" break="no"/>ris zelus atque inuidie. Accidens est quod aut ver
        <lb ed="#V" n="12" break="no"/>bis causaliter oboritur: vt hominum: aut proptur co
        <lb ed="#V" n="13" break="no"/>mestiones: vt iumentis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e317">
               <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>¶
               <ref>Boetius de consolatione li. 4. c. 7.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e321">Bonos
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>quis nisi stultissimus oderit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e327"> /
            <ref>Idem topi
        <lb ed="#V" n="16" break="no"/>corum libro 3.</ref> 
        <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e329">Ex arrogantia fit quisque odiosus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e335">
               <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>/
               <ref>Idem in musica li. i. c. i.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e339">Odiosa est dissimi
        <lb ed="#V" n="18" break="no"/>litudo atque contraria.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e345">
               <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>¶
               <ref>Cassiodorus epistolarum li. 10. e. 11.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e349">  </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e354">
               <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e358">/ De elatione odium concitatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e362">
               <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>¶
               <ref>Isidorus soliloquiorum. lib. 2. c. 23.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e366">Aliene
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>nequitie non serues dolorem. Odium a regno
        <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>dei seperat hominem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e374"> /
            <ref>45. c.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e376">Odium timor generat</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-d1e380">
               <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>¶
               <ref>Andreas ad gualterium li. 3.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d32366-Qd1e384">Nullus tanto
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>dilectionis alicui vel amicitie vinculo colli
        <lb ed="#V" n="26" break="no"/>gatur: si cognouerit ipsum pro sue vxoris vel
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>filie vel propinque instanter esse amore sollici
        <lb ed="#V" n="28" break="no"/>tum quoniam statim contraipsum nec accipiat: odii liuore mo
        <lb ed="#V" n="29" break="no"/>ueri et indignationis venena concipere.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
